title: Aliens are REAL & Keto is Dangerous - EP 2
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! New episodes EVERY Thursday!


This episode the Babes cover sleep apnea lifestyle, they sing about tequila, Chris being rusty at PT, Aliens are real and are on a government contract according to Haim Eshed, do aliens have gender and are they insecure?, former Mayor Bloomberg speaking spanish, Sal gets socks from Will Smith, Keto diet dangers, Sal breaks down the time he BOMBED on Kelly Ripa!
